<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>
  XQ Tech Solutions ("we," "our," or "us") operates the MyChoice Palakkad mobile and web
  application (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose,
  and safeguard your information when you use our App.
</p>
<p>
  MyChoice Palakkad is a local fashion discovery platform that connects clothing shops in
  Palakkad with customers. The App allows customers to browse products, contact shops via
  WhatsApp, leave reviews, and earn cashback rewards. Shop owners can list their products,
  receive customer analytics, and manage their storefront through subscription plans.
</p>
<p>
  By using MyChoice Palakkad, you agree to the collection and use of information in
  accordance with this Privacy Policy.
</p>

<hr />

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<h3>1. Personal Information</h3>
<p>When you register and use our App, we may collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and password for authentication</li>
  <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Profile photo, gender, and preferences you choose to provide</li>
  <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Your device location (GPS, network-based) to show nearby shops and relevant product listings</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Shop Owner Information</h3>
<p>If you register as a shop owner, we additionally collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Business Details:</strong> Shop name, address, contact number, WhatsApp number, and business category</li>
  <li><strong>Subscription Information:</strong> Plan details, payment history, and billing information</li>
  <li><strong>Product Listings:</strong> Product images, descriptions, pricing, and categories</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Search and Browsing Data</h3>
<p>We collect your activity within the App, including:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Search History:</strong> Keywords and filters you use to search for products or shops</li>
  <li><strong>Browsing Patterns:</strong> Products viewed, shops visited, categories explored, and time spent on listings</li>
  <li><strong>Interaction Data:</strong> Products saved, shared, or contacted via WhatsApp</li>
</ul>

<h3>4. Reviews and Ratings</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Product Reviews:</strong> Text reviews, star ratings, and images you submit after purchasing products</li>
  <li><strong>Shop Reviews:</strong> Feedback and ratings you provide for shops</li>
</ul>

<h3>5. Wallet and Transaction Data</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Cashback Records:</strong> Wallet balance, cashback earned, and redemption history</li>
  <li><strong>Purchase Verification:</strong> Information related to verified purchases for cashback eligibility</li>
</ul>

<h3>6. Device and Usage Information</h3>
<p>We automatically collect:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, unique device identifiers, and app version</li>
  <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Features accessed, timestamps, session duration, and interaction patterns</li>
  <li><strong>Notification Preferences:</strong> Settings for push notifications and alerts</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

<h3>For Customers</h3>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Provide Services:</strong> Display nearby shops, product listings, and enable WhatsApp-based contact with shop owners</li>
  <li><strong>Personalize Experience:</strong> Show relevant products and shops based on your location, search history, and browsing patterns</li>
  <li><strong>Manage Wallet:</strong> Track cashback earned from purchases and facilitate redemption at eligible shops</li>
  <li><strong>Enable Reviews:</strong> Allow you to post and view product and shop reviews</li>
  <li><strong>Send Notifications:</strong> Deliver deal alerts, cashback updates, and new product notifications</li>
</ol>

<h3>For Shop Owners</h3>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Analytics and Insights:</strong> Provide aggregated and anonymized customer search trends, popular product categories, demand patterns, and browsing analytics to help shop owners understand customer interests</li>
  <li><strong>Manage Listings:</strong> Enable product listing creation, updates, and inventory management</li>
  <li><strong>Subscription Management:</strong> Process subscription payments and manage feature access based on plan</li>
  <li><strong>Customer Engagement:</strong> Facilitate WhatsApp-based communication with interested customers</li>
</ol>

<h3>General</h3>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Improve the App:</strong> Analyze usage patterns to enhance features and user experience</li>
  <li><strong>Provide Support:</strong> Respond to your inquiries and technical issues</li>
  <li><strong>Ensure Security:</strong> Protect against unauthorized access, fraud, and maintain data integrity</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h2>Search Analytics and Shop Owner Insights</h2>
<p>
  <strong>Important:</strong> We collect customer search history and browsing data to generate
  analytics reports for shop owners. This helps shop owners understand what products
  customers are looking for in their area.
</p>
<p>The analytics shared with shop owners include:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Trending search keywords and product categories in their area</li>
  <li>Popular products and demand patterns</li>
  <li>Aggregated browsing trends (not individual user data)</li>
  <li>Customer engagement metrics for their listings</li>
</ul>
<p>
  <strong>We do NOT share individual customer identities, personal information, or
  individual search histories with shop owners.</strong> All analytics provided to shop
  owners are aggregated and anonymized.
</p>

<hr />

<h2>Cashback Wallet</h2>
<p>Our App includes a cashback wallet feature. Please note:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Cashback is earned when you make verified purchases from participating shops</li>
  <li>Wallet balance is <strong>not redeemable for real cash</strong> — it can only be used as a discount on future purchases</li>
  <li>Cashback earned from a specific shop can <strong>only be redeemed at that same shop</strong> — it is not transferable to other shops</li>
  <li>We store wallet balances, transaction history, and redemption records</li>
  <li>Wallet balances may expire as per the terms communicated in the App</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>Location Data</h2>
<p>We collect and use your location data to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Show shops and products near your current location</li>
  <li>Provide distance-based search results and sorting</li>
  <li>Generate location-based analytics for shop owners (aggregated, not individual)</li>
  <li>Improve local search relevance</li>
</ul>
<p>
  You can disable location access through your device settings, but this may limit
  the App's ability to show nearby shops and products.
</p>

<hr />

<h2>Data Storage and Security</h2>

<h3>Storage</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Cloud Storage:</strong> Your data is stored securely on Firebase (Google Cloud Platform) servers</li>
  <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Some data is cached locally on your device for offline access and performance</li>
  <li><strong>Data Sync:</strong> Information synchronizes between your device and cloud when connected to the internet</li>
</ul>

<h3>Security Measures</h3>
<p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Secure authentication via Firebase Authentication</li>
  <li>Encrypted data transmission (HTTPS/TLS)</li>
  <li>Access controls limiting data access to authenticated users only</li>
  <li>Shop owners can only access their own listing data and aggregated analytics</li>
  <li>Regular security assessments and updates</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
<p>We do <strong>NOT</strong> sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>
<p>We may share your information only in the following circumstances:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Shop Owner Analytics:</strong> Aggregated and anonymized search trends and browsing analytics are shared with subscribed shop owners to help them understand customer demand</li>
  <li><strong>WhatsApp Communication:</strong> When you choose to contact a shop via WhatsApp, your WhatsApp profile information is shared directly with the shop owner through WhatsApp's platform (governed by WhatsApp's privacy policy)</li>
  <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With trusted third-party services (Firebase/Google) that help us operate the App, subject to confidentiality agreements</li>
  <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law, court order, or government regulation</li>
  <li><strong>Protection of Rights:</strong> To protect the rights, property, or safety of XQ Tech Solutions, our users, or others</li>
  <li><strong>Business Transfers:</strong> In connection with any merger, acquisition, or sale of company assets (with prior notice)</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h2>Your Rights and Choices</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Access:</strong> View all your data stored in the App</li>
  <li><strong>Update:</strong> Modify your personal and profile information at any time</li>
  <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Enable or disable location sharing through device settings</li>
  <li><strong>Search History:</strong> Clear your search history within the App</li>
  <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Control push notification preferences in app settings</li>
  <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Stop using the App at any time</li>
</ol>
<p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@xqtechsolutions.com">admin@xqtechsolutions.com</a>.</p>

<hr />

<h2>Data Retention</h2>
<ul>
  <li>We retain your data as long as your account is active</li>
  <li>Upon account deletion request, we will delete your personal data within 30 days</li>
  <li>Shop owner subscription and billing data may be retained as required by tax and accounting laws</li>
  <li>Anonymized analytics data may be retained for improving our services</li>
  <li>Reviews may remain visible after account deletion in anonymized form</li>
  <li>Backup data may persist for up to 90 days before complete removal</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>
  MyChoice Palakkad is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not
  knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have
  collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.
</p>

